text: Gössenheim is a community in Main-Spessart in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (Administrative Community) of Gemünden am Main. ==Geography== ===Location=== Gössenheim is on the river Wern in the Würzburg Region. ===Constituent communities=== Gössenheim’s Ortsteile are Gössenheim and Sachsenheim. ==References== Category:Main-Spessart
title: Gössenheim
